description:
// O C C A S I O N
A couple of our friends and just finished a bikram yoga session and we were starving.

// F O O D
- Sweet potato wedges: big slicers that were deliciously crisp and fried so that the succulent sweet potato taste is in every wedge.

// S E R V I C E
- The cashier got our orders wrong twice and there was no condiments. We had to ask to put out the condiments.

// O T H E R
- Belly Burgers is in between a classic burger joint and a fast food restaurant.
